body:
**Dear Summoners,**

We are excited to announce two new sponsorships for our upcoming tournament in January!

**Gamestah** will be leading our stream & casting alongside **Aussie Gaming TV.**

[Sign up NOW!](http://pacificpeninsula.net/index.php?site=newsview&newsID=9)

Cheers,
_bollockz_
